description: An opposition party urges people to protest from their cars in order to maintain social distancing.
title: Coronavirus: Anti-lockdown car protest draws thousands
title_page: Coronavirus: Anti-lockdown car protest draws thousands - BBC News
maintext: The second division is also set to resume at the same time as the top flight, with reports suggesting the derby between Sevilla and Real Betis will be the first La Liga game to take place.
